c4dd702b-60d4-43f5-97da-71b0d4140e09	7ed95f9f-a84b-4a3a-9fc9-549e18efa22e	en	<p>Drag a pane from this list onto Custom Navigation or Pinned to make it appear in your sidebar. Panes already in use show a faded state but stay draggable so you can put them in a second slot.</p>	manual	\N	f	2026-05-02 02:49:15.806349+00	\N	2026-05-02 06:08:43.199311+00	\N	[]	[]
9ce8ed83-3828-43ec-961d-c62cdad70834	d28b0a7a-d589-409b-beeb-7d64edc39a43	en	<p>Your personal sidebar layout. Drag rows to reorder, drop a pane from Available Panes to add it, drop on a header row to start a new group.</p>	manual	\N	f	2026-05-02 02:49:15.806349+00	\N	2026-05-02 06:08:43.199311+00	\N	[]	[]
e27d0499-167a-47c9-a876-9fed9ce7cf82	054dbea0-c15a-4aab-b681-b610f56a2317	en	<p>Create a blank page (URL <code>/p/&lt;uuid&gt;</code>) that you can later fill with apps and charts. The page becomes available as a draggable pane in Available Panes immediately.</p>	manual	\N	f	2026-05-02 02:49:15.806349+00	\N	2026-05-02 06:08:43.199311+00	\N	[]	[]
